    <item>
      <title>特许学校和学院的市政债券市场陷入困境，创下历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/charter-schools-and-colleges-post-record-year-for-muni-distress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024 年，由于州和地方政府债务违约金额达到三年来的最高水平，大学和特许学校出售的市政债券陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/charter-schools-and-colleges-post-record-year-for-muni-distress</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 18:30:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>寒流冲击牛肉供应 活牛期货价格创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/cattle-futures-rise-to-record-with-cold-blast-to-hit-beef-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于气温下降和寒流天气即将袭击供应已经十分紧张的美国牛肉市场，活牛期货价格周四攀升至新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/cattle-futures-rise-to-record-with-cold-blast-to-hit-beef-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 18:10:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价上涨推高收益率，2025 年开年美国国债市场将重回熟悉状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/treasuries-start-2025-in-familiar-bind-as-oil-rally-lifts-yields</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2025 年伊始，美国国债价格出现了稳步上涨，但随后，失业救济申请人数减少、企业债券销售强劲以及油价上涨等经济复苏迹象逐渐显现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/treasuries-start-2025-in-familiar-bind-as-oil-rally-lifts-yields</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 17:07:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查显示尽管油价下跌，但美国石油老板支出增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/us-oil-bosses-see-spending-up-despite-lower-prices-survey-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管达拉斯联邦储备银行发布的最新能源调查显示，美国页岩油公司的高管们对油价的预期较低，但他们仍计划今年增加支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/us-oil-bosses-see-spending-up-despite-lower-prices-survey-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 17:06:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>福特、通用汽车开启 1 月份高等级债券热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/ford-general-motors-kick-off-january-high-grade-bond-binge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，一系列蓝筹公司开始在美国投资级一级债务市场发行债券，承销商准备迎接预计最繁忙的一月份债券销售月份之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/ford-general-motors-kick-off-january-high-grade-bond-binge</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 15:15:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国抵押贷款利率逼近 7%，房地产市场面临不祥之兆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/us-mortgage-rates-rise-to-highest-since-early-july-suppressing-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国抵押贷款利率攀升至接近7%，对试图进入房地产市场的购房者构成挤压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/us-mortgage-rates-rise-to-highest-since-early-july-suppressing-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
