    <item>
      <title>挪威天然气供应中断加剧俄罗斯天然气供应损失，欧洲天然气供应增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/european-gas-rises-following-loss-of-russian-flows-via-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于一条主要供应路线的中断、该地区北部地区气温降至冰点以及挪威出现意外中断，欧洲天然气价格在今年第一个交易日上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/european-gas-rises-following-loss-of-russian-flows-via-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 07:14:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伦敦金属交易所镍价跌至四年低点，2025 年开盘关注中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/metals-push-higher-with-focus-on-outlook-in-china-as-2025-opens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年第一个交易日，镍价跌至 2020 年以来的最低水平，铜价稳定在九个月低点附近，投资者正在权衡美元上涨的影响以及中国出台更多刺激措施的空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/metals-push-higher-with-focus-on-outlook-in-china-as-2025-opens</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 03:11:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员失去勇气，股市再次遭遇抛售：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市早盘的涨势崩盘，美国主要基准指数似乎将延续抛售行情，过去四个交易日股价下跌逾一万亿美元。特斯拉公司 (Tesla Inc.) 的年度汽车销量下滑导致圣诞节后股价暴跌近 20%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 22:58:34 GMT</pubDate>
